      "para_id": "Q001473.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Bau , the kind woman , the daughter of An , the lady of Iri-kug , his lady , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , built her city wall of Iri-kug ."
